    <description>Subjects conduct an aerobic exercise at 65-80% maximum oxygen consumption for 30 minutes each day, five days a week, totally for 6 months.Subsequently, moderate physical activity(3.0-6.0 MET s) at 150 min/wk for 6 months.</description>
    <arm_group_label>Intensive exercise</arm_group_label>
